# Plan: `sentry release` Command Group & CI Release Finalization

Ref: https://github.com/getsentry/cli/issues/600 (gap analysis — releases are the #1 critical gap)

## Summary

Add a full `sentry release` command group (list, view, create, finalize, delete, deploy, set-commits, propose-version) and a CI post-release step that creates, finalizes, and deploys Sentry releases with auto-commit association.

## Current State

- Build scripts upload sourcemaps tagged with a release version but never create/finalize a Sentry release object
- No `release` command group or API module exists
- The `@sentry/api` SDK already provides all needed release endpoints
- `.craft.yml` `postReleaseCommand` only bumps the dev version

